snippet.title: Manic Miners: A LEGO Rock Raiders remake  - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It's finally here! The full 1.0 release of Manic Miners has arrived, and brings creatures, new levels, visual level scripting, accessibility settings, a complete UI overhaul, and countless improvements. Rock Raiders has never been more alive. You will barely recognize the game from all the upgrades!

Dig in and play right now, for free! 
https://baraklava.itch.io/manic-miners

Music: 
LEGO Rock Raiders PC Original Soundtrack by Marl Boonyer - https://templesound.bandcamp.com/album/rockraiders-ep

Atmosdel from LEGO Rock Raiders - https://youtu.be/r00XdvCl93U
Track 1 from LEGO Rock Raiders for PS1 - https://youtu.be/1dnIst2QaQE
Piano tune - Just something I whipped up :)
